{
  "nbformat": 4,
  "nbformat_minor": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "kernelspec": {
      "name": "maxima",
      "display_name": "Maxima",
      "language": "maxima"
    },
    "aximar": {}
  },
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Inverse Problems: Recovering Physical Parameters\n\nGiven noisy measurements from a physical system, recover the underlying model parameters by minimizing data-model misfit. The **symbolic-numeric bridge** is central: we solve the governing ODE symbolically with `ode2()`, obtaining an analytic formula for the model predictions, then optimize these parameters numerically with `np_minimize`.\n\n1. **Spring-mass-damper** [S+N] — recover $k$ and $c$ from position data\n2. **Radioactive decay** [S+N] — recover half-life from count data\n3. **RLC circuit** — recover $R$ and $L$ from voltage response\n4. **Tikhonov regularization** — stabilizing ill-conditioned recovery",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "load(\"numerics\")$\nload(\"numerics-optimize\")$\nload(\"ax-plots\")$\n\n/* Finite-difference gradient helper */\nfd_gradient(f, x, eps) := block([nd, g],\n  nd : np_size(x), g : np_zeros([nd]),\n  for j : 0 thru nd - 1 do block([xp, xm],\n    xp : np_copy(x), np_set(xp, j, np_ref(x, j) + eps),\n    xm : np_copy(x), np_set(xm, j, np_ref(x, j) - eps),\n    np_set(g, j, (f(xp) - f(xm)) / (2 * eps))),\n  g)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 57,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 1. Spring-Mass-Damper System [S+N]\n\n### Symbolic Phase: Solving the ODE\n\nA damped harmonic oscillator with mass $m$, damping $c$, and spring constant $k$:\n$$m\\ddot{x} + c\\dot{x} + kx = 0, \\quad x(0) = x_0,\\; \\dot{x}(0) = v_0$$\n\nMaxima's `ode2()` solves this symbolically. The solution depends on the unknown parameters $(k, c)$.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Damped harmonic oscillator */\nassume(m > 0, k_spring > 0, c_damp > 0, 4*k_spring*m - c_damp^2 > 0)$\node_spring : m * 'diff(x, t, 2) + c_damp * 'diff(x, t) + k_spring * x = 0;",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 58,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "m\\,\\left({{d^2}\\over{d\\,t^2}}\\,x\\right)+{\\it c\\_damp}\\,\\left({{d}\\over{d\\,t}}\\,x\\right)+{\\it k\\_spring}\\,x=0"
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 58,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Solve with ode2 (underdamped case) */\nsol_general : ode2(ode_spring, x, t);",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 59,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "x=e^ {- \\left({{{\\it c\\_damp}\\,t}\\over{2\\,m}}\\right) }\\,\\left({\\it \\%k}_{1}\\,\\sin \\left({{\\sqrt{{{4\\,{\\it k\\_spring}}\\over{m}}-{{{\\it c\\_damp}^2}\\over{m^2}}}\\,t}\\over{2}}\\right)+{\\it \\%k}_{2}\\,\\cos \\left({{\\sqrt{{{4\\,{\\it k\\_spring}}\\over{m}}-{{{\\it c\\_damp}^2}\\over{m^2}}}\\,t}\\over{2}}\\right)\\right)"
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 59,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Apply ICs: x(0) = 1, x'(0) = 0, m = 1 */\nsol_ic : ic2(sol_general, t = 0, x = 1, 'diff(x, t) = 0)$\nsol_m1 : subst(m = 1, sol_ic)$\nx_sym : rhs(sol_m1);",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 60,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "e^ {- \\left({{{\\it c\\_damp}\\,t}\\over{2}}\\right) }\\,\\left({{{\\it c\\_damp}\\,\\sin \\left({{\\sqrt{4\\,{\\it k\\_spring}-{\\it c\\_damp}^2}\\,t}\\over{2}}\\right)}\\over{\\sqrt{4\\,{\\it k\\_spring}-{\\it c\\_damp}^2}}}+\\cos \\left({{\\sqrt{4\\,{\\it k\\_spring}-{\\it c\\_damp}^2}\\,t}\\over{2}}\\right)\\right)"
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 60,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "### Generating Synthetic Data\n\nWe choose \"true\" parameters $k = 8$ and $c = 0.5$ (underdamped), generate the true trajectory from the symbolic solution, then add noise.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* True parameters */\ntrue_params : [k_spring = 8, c_damp = 0.5]$\nx_true_sym : subst(true_params, x_sym)$\nprint(\"True solution:\", x_true_sym)$\n\n/* Sample at discrete times */\nn_obs : 40$\nt_obs : np_linspace(0, 6, n_obs)$\nt_list : np_to_list(t_obs)$\n\n/* Evaluate symbolic solution at observation times */\nx_true_nd : np_eval(x_true_sym, t, t_obs)$\n\n/* Add noise */\nnoise_level : 0.05$\nx_noisy : np_add(x_true_nd, np_scale(noise_level, np_randn([n_obs])))$\nprint(\"Generated\", n_obs, \"noisy observations\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 61,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "True solution:\n              %e^-(0.25*t)*(0.08873565094161139*sin(2.817356917396161*t)\n                           +cos(2.817356917396161*t))\nGenerated 40 noisy observations"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "ax_draw2d(\n  color=\"blue\", line_width=2, name=\"True x(t)\",\n  explicit(float(x_true_sym), t, 0, 6),\n  color=\"red\", marker_size=5, name=\"Noisy observations\",\n  points(t_list, np_to_list(x_noisy)),\n  title=\"Spring-Mass-Damper: Synthetic Data\",\n  xlabel=\"Time (s)\", ylabel=\"Position x(t)\",\n  grid=true, showlegend=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 62,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "application/x-maxima-plotly": [
